04:26.266 --> 04:31.431
<i>We, the students and faculty</i>
<i>of William Dawes Elementary,</i>

04:31.504 --> 04:36.305
<i>hereby bury this time capsule</i>
<i>in dedication of our new school,</i>

04:37.243 --> 04:39.211
<i>and we charge our descendents</i>

04:39.279 --> 04:43.909
<i>to open this vault of history</i>
<i>50 years from today.</i>

04:45.285 --> 04:48.948
<i>To the future and the promise that it holds.</i>

05:34.867 --> 05:36.129
